Unable to Add Items Dialog Box

Requires: Base Development System

This dialog box appears when LabVIEW is unable to add the items you selected to the project.

Use this dialog box to view information about the items you attempted to add that can help you resolve the errors.

This dialog box contains the following components:

  • Item List—Displays the items that LabVIEW was unable to add to the project.
  • Path—Displays the path on disk to the item you select from the Items List.
  • Details—Explains why LabVIEW was unable to add the item to the project.
